newsContent.newsTitle: Register now for June 2023 Community Meetup
newsContent.newsShortTitle: Register now for June 2023 Community Meetup
newsContent.newsDescription: NVIDIA and the LF AI & Data Foundation are pleased to sponsor the upcoming ONNX Community Meetup on June 28th at the NVIDIA campus in Santa Clara. Virtual attendees will be able to join the livestream and ask questions. The event will cover ONNX Community updates, lightning talks, and plenty of community networking. If you are using ONNX in your services and applications, building software or hardware that supports ONNX, or contributing to ONNX, you should attend! Last day to register for in-person is June 16th.
